 robustness, identification speed, bidirectional communication, reliability
 in different environment conditions, bunch detection and secured communication.
 Thus, RFID became the optimum solution for several applications where other
 identification technologies like bar-codes are unsuitable, for example,
 inventory tracking, supply chain management, automated manufacturing, etc
 
